data.text: @glassockclassic @abcnews And loved the rookie punter story.

@glassockclassic @abcnews Thanks @glassockclassic - no-one likes a hot phone.  Appreciate the explanation... keep up the good work and if you can air more Aussie sport, you'll make at least one of your many listeners happy.

@BruceRobertsWIN @abcnews and about a billion people world wide every week. It truly is now the world league and not just English football. In fact there's few Eng players in teams anymore. If we don't run it our phones run hot. I do appreciate it may not be your cup of tea though.

We do cover an enormous amount of sport that never gets a mention anywhere else (such as a story on Aus rookie punter Michael Dickson coming up next) As for the EPL it's the best league in the world watched by millions of Australians
